N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 363.4 - Fifty-two consecutive weeks

State Regulations

Fifty-two consecutive calendar weeks shall be computed
retroactively with respect to each day for which benefits are currently being
claimed. Notes
